snippet.title: Diana and her super fun day with Baby Doll
snippet.description:
Roma and Diana pretend play with toys for girls. Diana had a super fun day with the doll. She's as a mom for her dolls. The girl put her dolls on the bed, and protects their sleep.
Roma was played, mom asked him to look after his sisters. The boy looks after the little Baby doll-sisters and takes care of them. Good video for kids with Baby Dolls
